cs.CV, cs.IM, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image processing techniques for enhancing infrared (IR) radiation based superficial vein images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves signal processing techniques, which could fall under cs.IM (Image and Signal Processing). The use of low-performance computers and handheld devices suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves machine learning techniques for contrast enhancement, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
